  body.landing-page
    nav.navbar.navbar-transparent.navbar-fixed-top.navbar-color-on-scroll
      .container
        //- Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display
        .navbar-header
          button.navbar-toggle(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navigation-example')
            span.sr-only Toggle navigation
            span.icon-bar
            span.icon-bar
            span.icon-bar
          a(href='/')
            .logo-container
              .logo
                img(src='/img/logo.png', alt='Exnode Logo', rel='tooltip', title='<div class="small-tip"><b>Exnode</b> is a web app powered by <b>ExpressJs</b>, <b>NodeJs</b> and <b>Sweat</b></div>', data-placement='bottom', data-html='true')
              .brand  Exnode
        #navigation-example.collapse.navbar-collapse
          ul.nav.navbar-nav.navbar-right
            li
              a(href='/users', rel='tooltip',  title='<div class="small-tip">There are currently <b>12 Users</b> online</div>', data-placement='bottom', data-html='true') Users
            li
              a(href='/') About
            li
              a.btn.btn-simple.btn-white.btn-just-icon(href='#')
                i(class="icon ion-social-facebook")
            li
              a.btn.btn-simple.btn-white.btn-just-icon(href='#')
                i(class="icon ion-social-twitter")
            li
              a.btn.btn-simple.btn-white.btn-just-icon(href='#')
                i(class="icon ion-social-github")
    .wrapper 
      .header.header-filter
        .container
          .row
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
              .brand
                h1 Material Kit.
                h3 A Badass Bootstrap UI Kit based on Material Design.
      .main.main-raised
        .container
          .section.text-center.section-landing
            .row
              .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
                h2.title Let's talk product
                h5.description
                  | This is the paragraph where you can write more details about your product. Keep you user engaged by providing meaningful information. Remember that by this time, the user is curious, otherwise he wouldn't scroll to get here. Add a button if you want the user to see more.
            .features
              .row
                .col-md-4
                  .info
                    .icon.icon-primary
                      i.material-icons chat
                    h4.info-title First Feature
                    p
                      | Divide details about your product or agency work into parts. Write a few lines about each one. A paragraph describing a feature will be enough.
                .col-md-4
                  .info
                    .icon.icon-success
                      i.material-icons verified_user
                    h4.info-title Second Feature
                    p
                      | Divide details about your product or agency work into parts. Write a few lines about each one. A paragraph describing a feature will be enough.
                .col-md-4
                  .info
                    .icon.icon-danger
                      i.material-icons fingerprint
                    h4.info-title Third Feature
                    p
                      | Divide details about your product or agency work into parts. Write a few lines about each one. A paragraph describing a feature will be enough.
          .section.text-center
            h2.title Here is our team
            .team
              .row
                .col-md-4
                  .team-player
                    img.img-raised.img-circle(src='../img/avatar.jpg', alt='Thumbnail Image')
                    h4.title
                      | Gigi Hadid 
                      br
                      small.text-muted Model
                    p.description
                      | You can write here details about one of your team members. You can give more details about what they do. Feel free to add some 
                      a(href='#') links
                      |  for people to be able to follow them outside the site.
                    a.btn.btn-simple.btn-just-icon(href='#pablo')
                      i.fa.fa-twitter
                    a.btn.btn-simple.btn-just-icon(href='#pablo')
                      i.fa.fa-instagram
                    a.btn.btn-simple.btn-just-icon.btn-default(href='#pablo')
                      i.fa.fa-facebook-square
                .col-md-4
                  .team-player
                    img.img-raised.img-circle(src='../img/christian.jpg', alt='Thumbnail Image')
                    h4.title
                      | Christian Louboutin
                      br
                      small.text-muted Designer
                    p.description
                      | You can write here details about one of your team members. You can give more details about what they do. Feel free to add some 
                      a(href='#') links
                      |  for people to be able to follow them outside the site.
                    a.btn.btn-simple.btn-just-icon(href='#pablo')
                      i.fa.fa-twitter
                    a.btn.btn-simple.btn-just-icon(href='#pablo')
                      i.fa.fa-linkedin
                .col-md-4
                  .team-player
                    img.img-raised.img-circle(src='../img/kendall.jpg', alt='Thumbnail Image')
                    h4.title
                      | Kendall Jenner
                      br
                      small.text-muted Model
                    p
                      | You can write here details about one of your team members. You can give more details about what they do. Feel free to add some 
                      a(href='#') links
                      |  for people to be able to follow them outside the site.
                    a.btn.btn-simple.btn-just-icon(href='#pablo')
                      i.fa.fa-google-plus
                    a.btn.btn-simple.btn-just-icon(href='#pablo')
                      i.fa.fa-youtube-play
                    a.btn.btn-simple.btn-just-icon.btn-default(href='#pablo')
                      i.fa.fa-twitter
          .section.landing-section
            .row
              .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
                h2.text-center.title Work with us
                h4.text-center.description
                  | Divide details about your product or agency work into parts. Write a few lines about each one and contact us about any further collaboration. We will responde get back to you in a couple of hours.
                form.contact-form
                  .row
                    .col-md-6
                      .form-group.label-floating
                        label.control-label Your Name
                        input.form-control(type='text')
                    .col-md-6
                      .form-group.label-floating
                        label.control-label Your Email
                        input.form-control(type='email')
                  .form-group.label-floating
                    label.control-label Your Messge
                    textarea.form-control(rows='4')
                  .row
                    .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4.text-center
                      button.btn.btn-primary.btn-raised
                        | Send Message
